generic description: Durable Magnet - Our magnets are printed on wear resistant material with a solid, stiff magnetic backing. They are also fade resistant, and keep bright and sharp for a long time.
bullet point 1: Vibrant Printing - The colors are bright and vivid, so the design will stand out. We use fine tuned printing methods that ensure each magnet will look sharp and detailed.
bullet point 2: Strong Hold - Our magnets are easy to apply, and adhere effortlessly to any smooth, metal surface. They hold well and will not fall off easily.
bullet point 4: Multi Use - These are great for sticking a note or picture on a fridge. They are also perfect for safes, mini fridges, cabinets, and so much more! They can even be given as affordable gifts!

generic description: High Quality Vinyl - Our Stickers are printed on weather resistant Vinyl material. They can withstand the sun and rain and are very durable even outdoors.
bullet point 1: Vibrant Printing - The colors are bright and vivid, so the design will stand out. We use fine tuned printing methods that ensure each sticker will look sharp and detailed.
bullet point 2: Easy to Apply - Our stickers are easy to peel off and apply, and adhere effortlessly to any smooth, clean surface.
bullet point 4: Multi Use - The uses for these are endless. They are perfect for laptops, water bottles, notebooks, fridges, cars, and so much more!
